MBD REVENUE INCREASED REFLECTING GROWTH IN BUSINESS REVENUE, PARTIALLY OFFSET BY A DECLINE IN CONSUMER REVENUE. BUSINESS REVENUE INCREASED $1.2 BILLION OR 6%, WHICH REFLECTS 11% GROWTH IN OFFICE REVENUE FROM

SUBSCRIPTIONS AND

