SEEKING TO REVOKE THE UK PART OF THE EUROPEAN PATENT ASSERTED BY MOTOROLA IN GERMANY AGAINST THE ACTIVESYNC PROTOCOL. IN FEBRUARY 2012, MOTOROLA COUNTERCLAIMED ALLEGING INFRINGEMENT OF THE

