PATENT AND SEEKING DAMAGES AND AN INJUNCTION. A TRIAL TOOK PLACE IN DECEMBER 2012, AND THE COURT RULED THAT MOTOROLAS PATENT IS INVALID AND REVOKED. THE COURT ALSO RULED THAT THE PATENT,

