OF JUNE 30, 2013, APPROXIMATELY $3.6 BILLION OF THE APPROVED REPURCHASE AMOUNT REMAINED. THE REPURCHASE PROGRAM MAY BE SUSPENDED OR DISCONTINUED AT ANY TIME WITHOUT PRIOR NOTICE.

