INCLUDES A GOODWILL IMPAIRMENT CHARGE RELATED TO OUR OSD BUSINESS SEGMENT WHICH DECREASED NET INCOME BY $6.2 BILLION AND DILUTED EARNINGS PER SHARE BY

$0.73.

